(17, 'IT Support', 'P&G Indonesia', 'Kuningan, Jakarta', 'Rp15,000,000', 'Work From Office', 'Full Time', 'Mid Level', 'png.png', 'Our brands are trusted in millions of living rooms, kitchens, laundry rooms, and bathrooms—and have been passed down from generation to generation. We are the people behind the brands you trust, and we’re committed to making peoples’ lives better in small but meaningful ways, every day.\r\n\r\nAs P&G grows, we stay grounded in our purpose, values, and principles and a deep-rooted understanding between each other and our company that being our best and doing our best—for the people who buy our products, for one another, and for the world around us—will lead to mutual success.', 'We are seeking a Fleet Executive to join our global family. The role of the Fleet Executive is to ensure that Discova meets and exceeds its goals and operates successfully within the Fleet team.\r\n\r\nThis will involve delivering best-in-class service and memorable local experiences for the customer, Operationally, the role will be responsible for assigning and managing the fleet, handling operational issues, and continually providing feedback to management on risks and possible improvements of how we operate our products.', '-Manage the reservations system for transportation.\r\n-Work closely with the Reservation team to ensure all transfer logistics are fulfilled according to company SOPs \r\n-Effectively cooperate with OPS, Reservations, Product, Sales, Customer Experience and Suppliers for seamless daily operations and overall service improvements\r\n-Report to Fleet Team Leader for any required repair and inspections government health and safety regulations \r\n-Ensure all drivers follow Discova\"s and Ensure 24/7 support on the ground for client\"s complaints and incidents', '-Fluent in the local, national language and intermediate to advanced written and spoken English level\r\n  -A Degree in Hospitality or Tourism would be an advantage.', 'https://us.pg.com/'),
(18, 'Operations Manager', 'Google Indonesia', 'SCBD, Jakarta', 'Rp25,000,000', 'Hybrid', 'Full Time', 'Senior Level', 'google.png', 'At Google, our mission is simple: to organize the world’s information and make it universally accessible and useful. We strive to empower individuals and businesses with the tools and knowledge they need to navigate and thrive in an increasingly digital world.\r\n\r\nFounded in a garage by Larry Page and Sergey Brin in September 1998, Google has grown from a search engine into a global technology leader. Today, we offer a wide array of products and services designed to transform how people access information, communicate, and work.\r\n\r\nGoogle began as a research project by Larry and Sergey while they were Ph.D. students at Stanford University. They developed a new search engine that used links to determine the importance of individual pages on the World Wide Web. What started as an academic endeavor quickly evolved into a revolutionary way to find information, leading to the birth of Google Inc.\r\n\r\nFrom those humble beginnings, Google has expanded into many areas of technology. With the launch of products like Google Ads, Gmail, Google Maps, Android, and Chrome, we’ve continually innovated to make technology accessible and helpful for everyone.', 'We are seeking a Fleet Executive to join our global family. The role of the Fleet Executive is to ensure that Discova meets and exceeds its goals and operates successfully within the Fleet team.\r\n\r\nThis will involve delivering best-in-class service and memorable local experiences for the customer, Operationally, the role will be responsible for assigning and managing the fleet, handling operational issues, and continually providing feedback to management on risks and possible improvements of how we operate our products.', '-Manage the reservations system for transportation.\r\n-Work closely with the Reservation team to ensure all transfer logistics are fulfilled according to company SOPs \r\n-Effectively cooperate with OPS, Reservations, Product, Sales, Customer Experience and Suppliers for seamless daily operations and overall service improvements\r\n-Report to Fleet Team Leader for any required repair and inspections government health and safety regulations \r\n-Ensure all drivers follow Discova\"s and Ensure 24/7 support on the ground for client\"s complaints and incidents', '-Fluent in the local, national language and intermediate to advanced written and spoken English level\r\n  -A Degree in Hospitality or Tourism would be an advantage.', 'https://www.google.com/about/careers/applications/locations/jakarta/'),
(19, 'Financial Analyst', 'Gojek', 'Sudirman, Jakarta', 'Rp18,000,000', 'Work From Office', 'Full Time', 'Mid Level', 'gojek.png', 'Gojek adalah perusahaan teknologi terkemuka di Asia Tenggara yang didirikan oleh Nadiem Makarim, Kevin Aluwi, dan Michaelangelo Moran pada tahun 2010 di Jakarta, Indonesia. Berawal sebagai layanan transportasi motor panggilan, Gojek telah berkembang menjadi sebuah ekosistem super-app yang mencakup berbagai layanan on-demand, pembayaran digital, dan solusi keuangan. Dengan misi untuk memudahkan kehidupan sehari-hari dan memberdayakan masyarakat, Gojek menyediakan platform yang menghubungkan pengguna dengan berbagai layanan penting melalui satu aplikasi yang mudah digunakan. Aplikasi Gojek kini menawarkan lebih dari 20 layanan, termasuk transportasi, pengantaran makanan, belanja, pengiriman barang, dan layanan kebersihan, yang dirancang untuk memenuhi kebutuhan harian jutaan orang di seluruh Indonesia dan beberapa negara Asia Tenggara lainnya.\r\n\r\nDi inti Gojek adalah komitmen terhadap inovasi dan pemberdayaan komunitas. Kami memanfaatkan teknologi untuk mengatasi tantangan yang dihadapi oleh pengemudi, mitra usaha, dan konsumen, memberikan mereka akses ke peluang ekonomi yang lebih baik dan layanan yang lebih efisien. Misalnya, dengan GoRide dan GoCar, kami menyediakan solusi transportasi yang cepat dan terpercaya. Melalui GoFood, kami menjadi penghubung antara pelanggan dengan ribuan restoran dan penyedia makanan, sementara GoSend dan GoBox menawarkan layanan pengiriman barang yang fleksibel dan terjangkau. Selain itu, layanan GoPay kami memberikan solusi pembayaran digital yang aman dan mudah, memungkinkan transaksi yang lancar untuk kebutuhan sehari-hari.', 'We are seeking a Fleet Executive to join our global family. The role of the Fleet Executive is to ensure that Discova meets and exceeds its goals and operates successfully within the Fleet team.\r\n\r\nThis will involve delivering best-in-class service and memorable local experiences for the customer, Operationally, the role will be responsible for assigning and managing the fleet, handling operational issues, and continually providing feedback to management on risks and possible improvements of how we operate our products.', '-Manage the reservations system for transportation.\r\n-Work closely with the Reservation team to ensure all transfer logistics are fulfilled according to company SOPs \r\n-Effectively cooperate with OPS, Reservations, Product, Sales, Customer Experience and Suppliers for seamless daily operations and overall service improvements\r\n-Report to Fleet Team Leader for any required repair and inspections government health and safety regulations \r\n-Ensure all drivers follow Discova\"s and Ensure 24/7 support on the ground for client\"s complaints and incidents', '-Fluent in the local, national language and intermediate to advanced written and spoken English level\r\n  -A Degree in Hospitality or Tourism would be an advantage.', 'https://www.gojek.com/en-id/about'),
